{"tid":730038,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印航客機疑駕駛艙玻璃破裂緊急折返 乘客：架機搖到想嘔","createTime":"2018-07-05T05:27:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T21:03:51.000Z","uid":1221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7030ffb5c02048aaa8db0fa2817ceda021e6f416","tid":730038,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T05:27:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.dreamstime.com/b/%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E6%B3%A2%E9%9F%B3-dreamliner%E5%96%B7%E6%B0%94%E6%9C%BA-33697842.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.dreamstime.com%2Fb%2F%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E9%259F%25B3-dreamliner%25E5%2596%25B7%25E6%25B0%2594%25E6%259C%25BA-33697842.jpg&h=303956da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本港發生航機飛行途中疑遇惡劣天氣致駕駛艙玻璃破裂的驚險事故。印度航空一架原定由香港飛往日本大阪的AI314客機，今晨8時半載著約140名乘客由香港起飛，但40至50分鐘後在逾3萬呎高空遇惡劣天氣，乘客指客機「好飄&hellip;搖到想嘔」，消息人士指駕駛艙玻璃更疑出現裂痕，機師遂決定緊急折返本港。機場一度局部戒備，幸客機在10時35分安全著降，百多名乘客雖可放下心頭大石，卻未知何時可再出發，促航空公司盡快安排免行程泡湯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180705/large/1530766055_c129.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180705%2Flarge%2F1530766055_c129.jpg&h=0dcd1f92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n涉事的AI314印航客機是波音787 Dreamliner。根據flightradar24網站紀錄，該客機由香港飛往日本大阪，並於今晨約8時半在香港機場起飛，之後爬升至3.3萬呎的高空，但起飛後僅約50分鐘（約早上9時20分），即是當飛機駛至距離香港300多公里的香港與台灣之間的海域上空時，客機突然急轉右彎，在空中兜了4個圈，然後折返香港機場，並於早上約10時35分安全著陸。<br />\n<br />\n政府新聞處證實今晨約10時18分，機場曾就客機折返一事派出一部救護車作出局部戒備，但未有透露詳情。機場消息人士則指，印航客機機師曾向機場控制塔表示，駕駛艙玻璃出現裂痕，故需要緊急折返。另根據讀者提供客機著陸後相片，見到客機駕駛艙正前方其中一塊玻璃上有一些白色的痕跡，有機場人員懷疑是裂痕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180705/large/1530763338_c88c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180705%2Flarge%2F1530763338_c88c.jpg&h=74dacd6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n該客機上約140名乘客則「遊飛機河」，現時徬徨無助。乘客譚太與丈夫及兩名年幼子女今晨剛巧坐在渉事航班上，原準備往日本大阪玩6天。但譚太稱今晨8時半客機起飛後，發現高空雲層頗厚，天氣不好，她並感到感客機「好飄、好搖」。當空姐派發飛機餐給眾人享用後，機艙原已熄燈，讓乘客小睡休息。未料至早上9時許機艙突然再亮燈，機長並透過廣播指由於天氣問題，航班需要折返，乘客如譚太雖感無奈及掃興，但亦只有無奈接受。譚太稱疑因飛機飛行不穩定，回航時機上有BB不斷哭喊，<span style=\"color: red;\">譚太自己也是人生第一次有暈機浪及想作嘔的感覺，幸客機至大約10時半終安全降落香港機場。</span><br />\n但<span style=\"color: red;\">譚太稱機或機艙服務員從未詳細解釋客機折返原因</span>，乘客下機後需等候穿梭巴士前往候機地方，但未知何時可再出發，並擔心整日的行程泡湯，故<span style=\"color: red;\">她和乘客促請航空公司作出適當安排或<strong>補償</strong></span>。"},{"pid":"8fb8e8e7289405c543a98337e7d6bb98e1cbb591","tid":730038,"uid":47674,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T05:38:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/133818_67b5339c629bd50ccd1e2b23fda4ca51.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F133818_67b5339c629bd50ccd1e2b23fda4ca51.JPG&h=0853ee5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf98aa0eabc69f4ef4e2ada4bcf80971532aec98","tid":730038,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T05:54:55.000Z","msg":"仲以為係架機想嘔添  以為真係咁有趣搞到我入左黎 標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e2b54ceb50209d52608ace5659ba2f9f4dc5b1d","tid":730038,"uid":37661,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T05:58:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">她和乘客促請航空公司作出適當安排或補償。</span><br />\n<br />\n等退錢啦，邊有 Spare 機招呼你呀，仲要唔係日日有機經香港。"},{"pid":"44b686f9038933d309078629355861fca3ef1d26","tid":730038,"uid":176366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bf98aa0eabc69f4ef4e2ada4bcf80971532aec98","tid":730038,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T05:54:55.000Z","msg":"仲以為係架機想嘔添  以為真係咁有趣搞到我入左黎 標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T06:00:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c5b2c1d6a02db6ad84c3d58f6a665ae1554d225","tid":730038,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T06:07:49.000Z","msg":"想象吓平時喺街見到咖哩佬都覺得臭，仲要成個機艙都係咖哩佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75df6ff4fc6497119e8a10ac1f5e74dce4a20594","tid":730038,"uid":20658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T06:14:23.000Z","msg":"屌你老母有bb喊真係煩上加煩"},{"pid":"07f5340bafa8c2f0a1c98b6731e682df9f28537f","tid":730038,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fb8e8e7289405c543a98337e7d6bb98e1cbb591","tid":730038,"uid":47674,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T05:38:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/133818_67b5339c629bd50ccd1e2b23fda4ca51.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F133818_67b5339c629bd50ccd1e2b23fda4ca51.JPG&h=0853ee5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T06:14:56.000Z","msg":"唔係迫降中正機場咩"},{"pid":"d2683a690930fda64dbc87ac3d388506db7b09c0","tid":730038,"uid":31482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T06:18:32.000Z","msg":"今日咁嘅天氣部機好搖應該係正常事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"853fd4c5d10032210634a63483384cce20114860","tid":730038,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07f5340bafa8c2f0a1c98b6731e682df9f28537f","tid":730038,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fb8e8e7289405c543a98337e7d6bb98e1cbb591","tid":730038,"uid":47674,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T05:38:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/133818_67b5339c629bd